name: The Ticker Is ETH
description: The ticker is $ETH. We are a Meme Coin on Solana. Where Instant Transactions, Zero-Fees, and Community Engagement are Fostered. Where Cult meets Culture. We are a community that uplifts each other, where we share incredible memes, where we discuss trading setups, where we discuss investing knowledge, and where we can grow throughout the cycle together. At our core, we are a meme coin project, but we have greater long-term plans to explore LST options, NFT options, and hybrid token model options.
